**Add Reference Line**

*statline* argument is used to show the mean line.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
reactable(
  report,
  defaultPageSize = 13,
  columns = list(
    Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
    `Monthly Sales` = colDef(
      cell = react_sparkline(
        report,
        highlight_points = highlight_points(
          min = "red", max = "blue"),
        # include the mean reference line here
        statline = "mean"
        )
    )
  )
)
```

